description.narrative: The Transformative Monitoring for Enhanced Equity (TransMonEE) database for 2018 was completed by the BiH Agency for Statistics (BHAS), thereby strengthening social statistics for monitoring child rights. UNICEF and BHAS co-convened the SDGs Data Sub-Group, consisting of all the statistical institutes, government planning departments and UN agencies, which jointly identified a set of key indicators relevant for SDG monitoring in BiH. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:19/01/2020
